data.description: Your dream home is finally here! Beautiful 3-bedroom with loft home located in the Glennwilde Community is now on the market. You'll discover an impressive interior featuring high ceilings, neutral palette throughout, & tile flooring. Formal Model Home. The well-appointed kitchen showcases maple cabinets adorned with crown moulding, granite counters, stylish tile backsplash, built-in appliances, a pantry, & modern recessed lighting. The versatile loft with plush carpet offers endless possibilities! Primary bedroom boasts plantation shutters, a private bathroom with dual sinks, & a walk-in closet. Enjoy relaxing or host memorable gatherings in the wonderful backyard including a covered patio, built-in BBQ, & easy-care new turf and desert landscape! A few house from community pool and park.
